Title: Mister Knifey-Hands
Actors: Wendi McLendon-Covey, Jeff Garlin, George Segal, Sean Giambrone
Plot: Despite Beverly's wishes, Jackie's parents allow Adam to watch A Nightmare on Elm Street (1984) and a disagreement between the families ensues; Beverly faces off with horror icon Freddy Krueger; Erica realizes she's not as popular as she once was.
